     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="5"/>
   <head>To his deare friend the Author.</head>
   <l>HAue you not heard the melancholly note</l>
   <l>The Rauen sends from her Propheticke throte,</l>
   <l>The Lich-owles screcke, the dreadfull Thunder rore</l>
   <l>The Martiall Drum, men wallowing in their gore</l>
   <l>A mid-night passing Bell or Belmans Song,</l>
   <l>The raging Lionesse for her lost yong,</l>
   <l>So sound thy sacred Sonets in our eares</l>
   <l>Stirring vs vp with Musique to our feares.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>E. H.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
